# Title: Remote Code Execute via Winrm.vbs
# Author: Julia Fomina, oscd.community
# Date: 2020-10-07
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects an attempt to execute code or create service on remote host via winrm.vbs.
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1216
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_winrm_execution_via_scripting_api_winrm_vbs.yml

CommandLine="*winrm*" CommandLine="*invoke Create wmicimv2/Win32_*" CommandLine="*-r:http*" Image="*\\cscript.exe" OR OriginalFileName="cscript.exe"